&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core C++ Developer – Crypto High-Frequency Trading&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Selini:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selini is a global trading firm focused on systematic trading and venture investing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an exceptional &lt;strong&gt;Core C++ Developer&lt;/strong&gt; to contribute to the development and optimization of our &lt;strong&gt;high-performance trading systems&lt;/strong&gt;. This role focuses on building ultra-low-latency infrastructure, optimizing execution speed, and ensuring robust system reliability. The ideal candidate will have deep expertise in &lt;strong&gt;modern C/C++&lt;/strong&gt;, systems programming, and high-performance computing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and optimize &lt;strong&gt;low-latency, high-performance trading infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt; in &lt;strong&gt;modern C/C++ (latest standards)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement efficient and scalable &lt;strong&gt;trading algorithms, order execution, and risk management systems&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of exchange connectivity standards for &lt;strong&gt;market data and order entry&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize &lt;strong&gt;CPU performance, memory management, and multi-threaded applications&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with &lt;strong&gt;quant researchers, traders, and infrastructure engineers&lt;/strong&gt; to improve system performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Profile, benchmark, and debug real-time systems to minimize latency and maximize throughput.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain &lt;strong&gt;robust and fault-tolerant&lt;/strong&gt; system components for &lt;strong&gt;continuous trading operations&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expert-level proficiency in C++&lt;/strong&gt;, with a strong grasp of &lt;strong&gt;modern C++ features (C++17/20/23/26)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience in &lt;strong&gt;low-latency, high-performance systems programming&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of &lt;strong&gt;networking (TCP/UDP), concurrency, and multi-threading&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in &lt;strong&gt;Linux-based development&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;performance tuning&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with &lt;strong&gt;real-time, high-throughput systems&lt;/strong&gt; where performance is critical.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in &lt;strong&gt;crypto or traditional finance trading systems&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Soft Skills &amp;amp; Culture Fit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidates with exceptional academic or industry backgrounds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills and ability to work in &lt;strong&gt;high-pressure, real-time environments&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative team player who enjoys solving &lt;strong&gt;complex engineering problems&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re a close-knit team that values:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High ownership and initiative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity, intellectual honesty, and rapid learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear, direct communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working together toward shared goals — no ego, no politics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
