&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Selini:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selini is a leading crypto firm operating exclusively in the digital asset space. Our team brings together a deep blend of crypto-native talent and institutional finance experience, with expertise across research, technology, and infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selini Capital is seeking an experienced Crypto OTC Sales professional where you’ll serve as the primary point of contact for clients. The role combines financial markets expertise, sales acumen, and a deep understanding of digital assets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have the opportunity to have an impact on OTC growth, working closely with our best in class business development teams.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and grow the firm’s OTC operations alongside an international team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This includes client coverage as well as ongoing business development responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage your in-depth knowledge of the cryptocurrency market and trends to provide clients with actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure smooth OTC operations by working closely with local and global colleagues to provide consistent client coverage and support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the business development team to shape and execute the overall OTC sales strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize internal market research and commentary to enhance client engagement and deliver added value; the ability to independently generate market insights is a strong asset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the firm at industry conferences, events, and networking opportunities to grow the client base and stay informed on evolving market dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid experience from previous Crypto OTC Sales or broking role, including execution and pricing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional understanding of cryptocurrency markets and projects/assets and trends/narratives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A well-established OTC client network which includes strong relationships with foundations, HNWIs, funds and family offices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with proven track record in client facing and business development roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum Bachelor’s degree in a quantitative or related field, such as Mathematics, Physics, Computer Science, Economics, Finance, or Engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
